 ('1', '1', 'en_ca', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-09-26 20:51:47', '2015-09-26 20:51:47', '5067ca9b-e4f8-47f5-8e65-89aa43f4abbf'),
 ('2', '2', 'en_ca', 'Konnexis', '<p>It’s true, this site doesn’t have a whole lot of content yet, but don’t worry. Our web developers have just installed the CMS, and they’re setting things up for the content editors this very moment. Soon Konnexis.dev will be an oasis of fresh perspectives, sharp analyses, and astute opinions that will keep you coming back again and again.</p>', 'Global Market Leaders in Sterilization Control and Monitoring Systems', 'Advanced monitoring solutions designed for the sterilization industry, for growth, production efficiency and the long term.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-09-26 20:51:48', '2015-10-17 15:29:38', '6a7e834e-4619-423d-a8fe-a60013784d76'),
 ('3', '3', 'en_ca', 'We just installed Craft!', '<p>Craft is the CMS that’s powering Konnexis.dev. It’s beautiful, powerful, flexible, and easy-to-use, and it’s made by Pixel & Tonic. We can’t wait to dive in and see what it’s capable of!</p><!--pagebreak--><p>This is even more captivating content, which you couldn’t see on the News index page because it was entered after a Page Break, and the News index template only likes to show the content on the first page.</p><p>Craft: a nice alternative to Word, if you’re making a website.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-09-26 20:51:49', '2015-10-03 23:14:07', '92cc1d6a-2e07-4253-b7d9-db2d9584e878'),
 ('4', '4', 'en_ca', 'Home Header', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-10-03 15:07:35', '2015-10-03 15:07:49', '83f48ce3-98d1-496a-a1b0-bbae3664ece7'),
 ('5', '5', 'en_ca', 'Medical Device Manufacturers', NULL, NULL, 'Konnexis helps you ensure that your products are efficiently and properly sterilized through integration of data management systems in Irradiator and chamber control. Our systems include product tracking, specification management, and process monitoring. We offer seamless integration with our customers’ MRP systems, providing enterprise-wide access to on-the-floor information in real time.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-10-03 15:33:54', '2015-10-12 19:44:17', 'e80f4875-5b5f-4f87-a2cd-9cdbe7be10d7'),
 ('6', '6', 'en_ca', 'Sterilization Services Contractors', NULL, NULL, 'Konnexis provides competitive advantage through affordable scalability through integration of data management in Irradiator and chamber control. Our systems include product tracking, specification management, and process monitoring. We offer seamless integration with our customers’ MRP systems, providing enterprise-wide access to on-the-floor information in real time.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-10-03 15:34:10', '2015-10-12 19:43:59', '1a99290f-dfdc-423b-a959-08f0490e2b06'),
