 ('13', '13', 'en_ca', 'About Us', NULL, NULL, 'Originally from Slovakia, Peter Veselovsky came to Canada to study process engineering at the University of Toronto. As an avid skier he fell in love with Canadian winters and decided to stay. While working with Nordion leading their Irradiator Control Systems group and their Radiation Therapy Controls group he realized that the level of integration into large company systems was severely lacking. Peter believed that it was possible to integrate sterilization control systems with manufacturer’s complex work flows and still have highly effective and safe systems that would meet stringent regulatory standards. With this aim, Peter formed Konnexis in 2000 and now, with his hand picked team, provides control systems and integration services for sterilization systems of all kinds around the world.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-10-03 15:36:49', '2015-10-18 23:25:31', '4cc639ce-af66-4c6a-b5a6-c36f973da0c3'),
 ('14', '14', 'en_ca', 'Ron Nyegard', '<p>Konnexis continues to provide excellent consulting, system development, and end-user support services to STERIS Isomedix Services. With over a 6-year business relationship, we have used Konnexis resources for development and implementation of our ERP application, business-to-business web services, customer web portal, and various process control and monitoring systems for both gamma and ethylene oxide processing. Their system’s expertise has delivered innovative solutions to our business requirements, resulting in positive impacts on our daily operations and our overall customer satisfaction ratings.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Director of Operations Systems Development at STERIS Isomedix Services', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-10-03 18:33:38', '2015-10-03 18:33:38', 'a36a794e-ec58-4b28-a9e0-5ec23c1a0d7d'),
 ('15', '15', 'en_ca', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'sales@konnexis.com', '1-613-599-7371 x223', '300 March Road, Suite 102, Kanata, ON K2K 2E2', 'https://twitter.com/Konnexis', 'http://www.linkedin.com/company/konnexis', 'http://www.google.com', '2015-10-03 18:37:49', '2016-01-04 00:27:00', 'e03dbc54-1d2e-499b-a41c-00765e8aca84'),
 ('16', '16', 'en_ca', 'Kitchen Sink', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-10-03 21:26:13', '2015-10-03 21:26:13', 'b3890c6d-5d5a-4672-be10-8bf87d53090f'),
 ('17', '17', 'en_ca', 'Integrated Control Systems', '<p>Konnexis’ control systems do more than simply monitor your sterilization process.  This is because our systems are fully integrated with product tracking and process monitoring!  Read <a title=\"Why Konnexis?\" href=\"http://www.konnexis.com/why-integrate/\">About Us&gt;&gt;Why Konnexis?</a> to find out about the benefits of our systems.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-10-03 22:39:22', '2015-10-03 23:08:41', 'e34a107e-8150-4ee7-af0d-2feeef542223'),
