 ('25', '13', '3', '1', 'en_ca', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"About Us\",\"slug\":\"about-us\",\"postDate\":1443886560,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"5\":[\"4\"],\"7\":\"\",\"4\":\"Originally from Slovakia, Peter Veselovsky came to Canada to study process engineering at the University of Toronto. As an avid skier he fell in love with Canadian winters and decided to stay. While working with Nordion leading their Irradiator Control Systems group and their Radiation Therapy Controls group he realized that the level of integration into large company systems was severely lacking. Peter believed that it was possible to integrate sterilization control systems with manufacturer\\u2019s complex work flows and still have highly effective and safe systems that would meet stringent regulatory standards. With this aim, Peter formed Konnexis in 2000 and now, with his hand picked team, provides control systems and integration services for sterilization systems of all kinds around the world.\"}}', '2015-10-12 19:38:26', '2015-10-12 19:38:26', 'dab46263-3c13-4db4-ba48-72802a0e82c6'),
 ('26', '13', '3', '1', 'en_ca', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"About Us\",\"slug\":\"about-us\",\"postDate\":1443886560,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"5\":[\"4\"],\"7\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"twoColumnText\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"leftColumnText\":\"<h2>Dedicated to the Sterilization Industry<\\/h2><p>Konnexis Inc. provides process control systems specifically for the sterilization industry delivering advanced and expert control and monitoring solutions for growth, production efficiency, and a future-proof system. Since 2000, Konnexis Inc. has grown to establish an international presence within the sterilization industry partnering with some of the world\\u2019s largest <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/konnexis.dev\\/sterilization-services-contractors#entry:6\\\">contract sterilization companies<\\/a> and <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/konnexis.dev\\/medical-device-manufacturers#entry:5\\\">medical device manufacturers<\\/a>.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"rightColumnText\":\"<h2>Global Market Leaders in Sterilization Control Systems<\\/h2><p>Konnexis is a global market leader of modern sterilization control systems. We have a range of proven solutions that have undergone rigorous testing to provide you with a reliable and dependable solution for any sterilization modality. Konnexis was selected as the control system for the world\\u2019s first high volume industrial sterilization x-ray facility. Our control systems are being used throughout the world which <strong>sterilize over 1 million pallets per year.<\\/strong>\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"white\"}}},\"4\":\"Originally from Slovakia, Peter Veselovsky came to Canada to study process engineering at the University of Toronto. As an avid skier he fell in love with Canadian winters and decided to stay. While working with Nordion leading their Irradiator Control Systems group and their Radiation Therapy Controls group he realized that the level of integration into large company systems was severely lacking. Peter believed that it was possible to integrate sterilization control systems with manufacturer\\u2019s complex work flows and still have highly effective and safe systems that would meet stringent regulatory standards. With this aim, Peter formed Konnexis in 2000 and now, with his hand picked team, provides control systems and integration services for sterilization systems of all kinds around the world.\"}}', '2015-10-12 19:42:29', '2015-10-12 19:42:29', '400480b9-4004-4245-be31-0e999dcb4ccb'),
