 ('4', '25', 'en_ca', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<h2>Dedicated to the Sterilization Industry</h2><p>Konnexis Inc. provides process control systems specifically for the sterilization industry delivering advanced and expert control and monitoring solutions for growth, production efficiency, and a future-proof system. Since 2000, Konnexis Inc. has grown to establish an international presence within the sterilization industry partnering with some of the world’s largest <a href=\"{entry:6:url}\">contract sterilization companies</a> and <a href=\"{entry:5:url}\">medical device manufacturers</a>.\r\n</p>', '<h2>Global Market Leaders in Sterilization Control Systems</h2><p>Konnexis is a global market leader of modern sterilization control systems. We have a range of proven solutions that have undergone rigorous testing to provide you with a reliable and dependable solution for any sterilization modality. Konnexis was selected as the control system for the world’s first high volume industrial sterilization x-ray facility. Our control systems are being used throughout the world which <strong>sterilize over 1 million pallets per year.</strong>\r\n</p>', 'white', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2015-10-12 19:42:29', '2015-10-18 23:25:31', '6f7a3ff3-3dc3-41ae-b9eb-f84289dda18f'),
 ('5', '26', 'en_ca', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'titleBar', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2015-10-17 13:28:57', '2015-10-17 18:46:39', 'b8a79a53-7e93-48ab-938f-ca1b6bec7dfa'),
 ('7', '28', 'en_ca', 'white', 'Global Market Leaders', '<p>Headquartered in Ottawa, Canada, Konnexis is a global market leader of modern sterilization control systems.  Since 2000 they have provided both Medical Device and Sterilization Contractors a range of unique and proven solutions for any sterilization modality; EtO, Gamma, X-ray, and E-Beam. Their control systems are being used throughout the world to sterilize over 1 million pallets per year.\r\n</p>', 'About', 'right', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2015-10-17 14:50:53', '2015-10-17 15:29:38', '619e363d-d386-49e9-8b87-8cc280000290'),
 ('8', '29', 'en_ca', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'overlay', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2015-10-17 14:50:53', '2015-10-17 15:29:39', '9c44cf29-527a-4e46-b0dd-61e424e5ffc4'),
 ('9', '30', 'en_ca', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Products & Services', '<p>We have a range of proven solutions that have undergone rigorous testing to provide you with a reliable and dependable solution for any sterilization modality. Our control systems are being used throughout the world which sterilize over 1 million pallets per year.\r\n</p>', 'grey', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2015-10-17 14:59:51', '2015-10-17 15:29:39', '581ff60d-c672-4de5-8b3a-cf189fdd1117'),
 ('10', '31', 'en_ca', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'titleBar', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2015-10-17 14:59:51', '2015-10-17 15:29:39', '96cdb388-5d33-469c-8428-61f103dad1a0'),
